    • Uses of Wordsi in edu.ucla.sspace.wordsi

      Classes in edu.ucla.sspace.wordsi that implement Wordsi 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  BaseWordsi
      This base class accepts or rejects key words based on a set of acceptedWords and dispatches calls to a ContextExtractor so that Wordsi sub-classes will be called with each generated vector.
      class  EvaluationWordsi
      An Wordsi implementation to be used for evaluations.
      class  StreamingWordsi
      A Wordsi implementation that utilizes streaming, or online, clustering algorithms.
      class  WaitingWordsi
      A Wordsi implementation that performs batch clustering.
